## Merak Trip Planner Agent

This repo now includes a minimal example of building a travel-planning agent using the [OpenAI Agents Python SDK](https://openai.github.io/openai-agents-python/).

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.11
- An OpenAI API key (`OPENAI_API_KEY`)

### Setup
```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### Run the Trip Planner
Provide the traveler details either as CLI arguments or via stdin.

```bash
export OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
python scripts/run_trip_planner.py "Plan a spring honeymoon in Japan focused on culture and food."
```

### Tests
```bash
pytest
```
